Package space.sunqian.fs

package space.sunqian.fs
The root package of fs, provides root supports for fs:

Global kits:

  • Fs: the core utilities kit;
  • FsLoader: the loader for implementations of fs;
Sub-packages for specific functions:
  • space.sunqian.fs.base
  • space.sunqian.fs.app
  • space.sunqian.fs.cache
  • space.sunqian.fs.codec
  • space.sunqian.fs.collect

  • space.sunqian.fs.io
  • space.sunqian.fs.net

  • space.sunqian.fs.reflect

    space.sunqian.fs.io
    Provides utilities and interfaces for IO related, including subpackages.
    space.sunqian.fs.net
    Provides utilities and interfaces for network, such as Http client, TCP client and server, UDP sender and server.
    space.sunqian.fs.object
    This package and its subpackages provide various object related operations; space.sunqian.fs.object.data: Parses and manipulates objects as data entities; space.sunqian.fs.object.convert: Converts objects into different types;
